		"title": "Relational Heatmap [SPAC] [DMAP]",
		"instructions": "Relation Heatmap displays the relations between source and target annotation labels. A relationship is defined as a unique pair of values, one from the source annotation and one from the target annotation. Please refer to DUET Documentation and GitHub Documentation for further information."
